#: data/core/units/saurians/Soothsayer.cfg:77
#: data/core/units/saurians/Augur.cfg:76 data/core/units/saurians/Augur.cfg:77
#: data/core/units/saurians/Oracle.cfg:76
#: data/core/units/saurians/Oracle.cfg:77
